Description: lightweight ASGI framework / toolkit (Avalan PPA transitive)
 Starlette is the minimal ASGI framework that FastAPI is built on
 top of. Packaged for the Avalan PPA because FastAPI's `vendors`
 stack requires `starlette >= 0.46.0` and Noble's archive carries
 0.36.x; pinned at the current 1.0.0 release.
